# Power Apps Excel CRUD Application

## Overview

This project is a low-code business application built using Microsoft Power Apps with Excel as the data source.

The application allows users to manage records stored in Excel without directly editing the spreadsheet. It demonstrates how Power Apps can be used to build business applications quickly using Excel.

## Features

- View Records
- Add New Records
- Search Records
- Edit Existing Records
- Delete Records
- User-Friendly Interface
- Excel as Data Source
- Real-Time Data Updates

## Technologies Used

- Microsoft Power Apps
- Microsoft Excel
- Microsoft Power Platform

## How It Works

1. Excel file is connected as a data source.
2. Power Apps displays the records.
3. Users can search for existing records.
4. Users can add new records.
5. Existing records can be updated.
6. Records can also be deleted.


